<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197368>
    bibo:endPage "68" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "61" ;
    bibo:volume "2570" ;
    dc:creator "Ng, Peter K. L.; Tri, Ngo Van" ;
    dc:date "2010" ;
    dc:title "Solenotheres prolixus, a new genus and new species of pinnotherid crab (Crustacea: Decapoda: Brachyura) associated with the razor clam, Solen corneus Lamarck, 1818 (Solenidae) in Vietnam" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197369>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197370>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197371> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197369>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Solenotheres prolixus, new genus, new species, holotype ovigerous female, cl 4.40 mm, cw 6.58 mm (ZRC), southern Vietnam. A, overall view; B, frontal view of carapace; C, ventral view of carapace." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197369/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197370>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Solenotheres prolixus, new genus, new species, holotype ovigerous female, cl 4.40 mm, cw 6.58 mm (ZRC), southern Vietnam. A, dorsal view of carapace; B, frontal view of carapace showing orbits, antennules and antennae; C, left MXP 3 (setae not drawn); D, MXP 3 palp, drawn from angle to show position of dactylus on propodus; E, left cheliped (setae not drawn); F, abdominal somites 5, 6 and telson. Scales: A = 1.0 mm; B – F = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197370/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197371>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Solenotheres prolixus, new genus, new species, holotype ovigerous female, cl 4.40 mm, cw 6.58 mm (ZRC), southern Vietnam. A – D, right P 2 – P 5, respectively (setae not drawn); E, left P 3 (setae not drawn). Scales = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197371/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

